      },
      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/kitab-al-ghayba-numani:2:11:10",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/11/10",
      "text": [
        ": هلك أصحاب المحاضير، ونجا المقربون، وثبت الحصن على أوتادها. إنّ بعد الغمّ فتحاً عجيباً."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(10) Muhammad bin Hammam and Muhammad bin al-Hasan bin Muhammad bin Jumhoor narrated from al-Hasan bin Muhammad bin Jumhoor from his father from Suma’a bin Mihran from Salih bin Maytham and Yahya bin Sabiq that Abu Ja’far al-Baqir (as) had said: “The hasteners will perish and those nearest to Allah will be saved! After distress there will be a wonderful deliverance!”"
        ]
      }
    },
